        <item>
            <title>【评测】小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 开箱评测，预载 Google TV OS 可装 APP + QD – Mini LED 面板亮度对比度更胜从前 + 设计走平实路线风格一般</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/17/mi-sminiled652025-review/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi-sminiled652025-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/17/mi-sminiled652025-review/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 14:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[家居无线]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mi S Mini LED 2025]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能显示屏]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1281998</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去到年底，不少品牌都纷纷推出自家的新一代电视，小米早前亦推出了新一代，采用全新 QD – Mini LED 面板的智能显示屏：小米 S Mini LED 2025，笔者就借得它的 65 吋版本，究竟采用新面板的这部智能显示屏表现如何？就让 Edward 为 unwire.hk 读者们实测一下吧。</p><h2>为何称「智能显示屏」？内有原因</h2><p>众所周知，小米在香港早已有推出智能电视产品，但今次推出的小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 为何称为「智能显示屏」而非「智能电视」？其实原因只有一个，就是因为它没有内建电视调频器（TV Tuner），直接点说就是没有内建电视天线，换言之大家是不能将天线插入它并欣赏电视讯号直播的，与之前推出的小米电视系列是有不同，这一点大家在入手时一定要留意。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002-694x303.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="303" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002-694x303.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001-694x215.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="215" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001-694x215.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/mi_001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲上面两个撷自官方规格的部分，第一张是来自小米电视，而第二张是来自今次这部小米智能显示屏，大家可以见到智能显示屏确实写著未设天线接口，而小米电视就设有 ATV / DTMB 调谐器，这就是为何今次这件新产品并非称为智能电视而是智能显示屏的主因。</p><h2>预载 Google TV OS 弥补没内建天线损失</h2><p>虽然如此，但大家依然可以透过小米 S Mini LED 65 2025 欣赏电视直播，原因是它是内建了 Google TV OS 的智能显示器，它内建了 Play Store 商店，用家只要透过 Play Store 就可以安装不同电视台的自家 APP，笔者试用过，由电视台的 myTV Super（TVB）、ViuTV，到串流影片平台 Netflix、Disney+、YouTube 等都可以安装及使用得到，尤其是电视台的 APP，只要注册后就可以欣赏电视直播，与大家在手机、平板或电脑上浏览电视直播方法是一样的，虽然相比接收天线讯号会有少许延迟（大约 10 多 20 秒左右），但相信对于绝大部分用家来说，应该也不会太介意吧。不过最重要是预载了 Google TV OS 可以直接装 APP，令大家无需再接驳 TV Stick 已可用到智能电视的功能，变相省回一个 HDMI 端子可以接驳其他装置，使用上亦更加方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121845.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲S Mini LED 2025 预载了 Android TV 14 版本的 Google TV OS，不像之前小米推出的智能电视般需要插入 TV Stick 才可以进入 Google TV 安装软件。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048-694x416.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="416" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048-694x416.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_121048.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲S Mini LED 2025 的主介面采用了近乎原生的 Google TV 介面，而操控只需要透过附送的遥控器即可。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511-694x402.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="402" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511-694x402.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123511.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123336.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲虽然没有电视天线，但透过 Google TV，就已可通过不同电视台的 APPS，欣赏各大电视台的电视直播，不过比较可惜的是暂时只可欣赏 TVB 及 ViuTV，有线的开电视及香港电台就由于没有相关 APPS，所以就未能在此电视上欣赏直播了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282024" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908-694x403.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="403" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908-694x403.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204908.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282025" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205045.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者试过透过 myTV Super 及 ViuTV APP 欣赏两个电视台的直播，是完全没有问题的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/002.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/001.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然要解决此问题亦不难，由于 S Mini LED 2025 支援 Miracast 无线投影功能，大家只需要在手机或平板开启开电视或 RTHK 的 APP，之后使用 Miracast 无线投屏到智能显示屏上，就可以间接在大荧幕欣赏这两个电视台的电视直播了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282020" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205345.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282021" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205435.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282023" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342-694x389.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342-694x389.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204342.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282022" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_122643.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然作为支援安装 APPS 的平台，要在 S Mini LED 2025 上欣赏 Netflix、Disney+、Max、甚至欣赏 Now TV 收费电视频道的节目也可以，而由于显示屏本身支援 4K 解析度及 Dolby Vision 格式，所以欣赏相关格式影片自然亦没问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_204502.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲遥控本身亦设有 Netflix、YouTube 及 Amazon Prime Video 的独立启动键，亦可按下 APPS 按键进入程式列表。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282026" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205336.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282027" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205511.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者实测欣赏 Netflix 及 Disney+ 上的串流影片，流畅度十分高，画质亦十分不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282028" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248-694x420.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="420" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248-694x420.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123248.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲以 Now TV APP 欣赏英超直播亦完全无难度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282029" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123629.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282030" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635-694x408.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="408" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635-694x408.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123635.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，用家亦可安装 VLC for Android 或 MX Player，浏览抄写到电视内或接驳到电视的 USB 手指内的本地影片。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282032" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607-694x418.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="418" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607-694x418.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123607.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲除了影片平台外，其实用家亦可安装其他多媒体平台，例如：可以安装 Spotify 或 KKBOX 欣赏音乐，或者安装不同 Tuner 程式收听电台节目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282033" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205631.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲透过 Tunein Radio 就已可收听香港电台的直播节目。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282034" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205713.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_205731.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者亦试过在显示屏上收听 Spotify 音乐，甚至可以开启「歌词」功能，大家就可以与亲友在大荧幕上唱 K 了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241029_123652.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者亦发现大家可以在智能显示屏上安装 VPN 软件，暂时见到有 NordVPN 及 SurfShark 两个较热门的选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856-694x394.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212856.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544-694x401.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="401" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544-694x401.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213544.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282040" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232-694x411.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="411" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232-694x411.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213232.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者试过在 S Mini LED 2025 上可以成功使用 VPN APP 连线到美国或英国等其他国家的伺服器，之后就可以看到香港睇不到，但在其他国家可以看到的节目。例如：在英国 Netflix 上可以看到 Harry Porter 电影，但笔者发现在香港的 Netflix 上就看不到了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959-694x409.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="409" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959-694x409.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_212959.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1282042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218-694x410.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="410" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218-694x410.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/img_20241216_213218.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外要知道是否成功使用 VPN 连线并进入海外的 Netflix 伺服器十分简单，只需要看影片简介上方的评级标志就可以了：第一张是美国的，第二张就是英国的。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
